  title: Eyes on the Enemy
  body: "Look around freely with the camera. When you\u2019re ready to fight, lock
    on to a target with T to keep them centered.\n\nWhile locked on, flick the camera
    to switch between targets. Lock breaks if your target dies, moves too far, or
    loses line of sight."
